# Guts Scoring iOS — Cursor rules

- This repo is **independent** from `GutsScoring` (Android). Do not edit Android unless the user explicitly asks.
- Read `docs/HANDOFF.md` and `docs/STATUS.md` at the start of substantial iOS work.
- API contract: `Guts-App-V5/docs/mobile-api/openapi.yaml`; production base URL `https://api.usaguts.com`.
- Match Android **behavior** using `docs/ANDROID_PARITY.md`; implement in Swift/SwiftUI.
- After changing `project.yml`, remind user to run `xcodegen generate` on Mac.
- Offline-first: local persistence before sync (mirror Android Room + outbox pattern).
